<br>
I also used MLA in my 12th grade English class on a paper that I got a 99 on, but just because it's taught somewhere doesn't mean it's the only way, or the right way.<br>
<br>
Everyone's right! Shut up! Stop sounding and looking stupid, but if you do, do it gracefully!<br>
