<br>
In case you need validation of that particular point of view, here's an example:<br>
<br>
&quot;gonna have to try a bit harder as for knowing everything was i ever wrong about anything? The blaming the wizard thing is off base i usually just blamed the puller dosent matter if he single pulled a green to the group must be his fault if we died : ), and the chronic masturbation only need one hand to click the CH hot key. &quot;<br>
<br>
Do I understand what he's trying to say?  Sure.  Did it make my brain hurt to try to decipher his Cro-Magnon gibberish?  A little.  Is he as much of an idiot in real life as he appears to be from that collection of run-ons and grammar errors?  Probably.<br>
<br>
/shrug<br>
<br>
Either way, it doesn't change my world, and provides some mild entertainment...until I realize that he'll probably still end up graduating from high school somehow, despite his 5th grade reading and writing level, and he'll probably end up being the jackass serving me my fries at Burger King and complaining about how messed up the country is and he got screwed over by &quot;the system.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=steaalinstuff>Steaalin Stuff</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Egging EW</span><br>  Posts: 271<br> <font color=#628CBC>(1/30/03 2:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=476.topic&index=79>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: .</span><hr size=1> d00d klol hoo lurned u 2 tolk???????kk hehe si kewl  bey. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=erradicatedthoughts>Erradicated Thoughts</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Riding the Planes</span><br>  Posts: 927<br> <font color=#628CBC>(1/30/03 2:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=476.topic&index=80>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: .</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>It is akin to using incredibly complex words, they convey the same message, in theory, but in practice, due to lack of knowledge, they do not.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
